      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s looking for a great new home! It\u2019s been well-loved and is in really solid shape\u2014super reliable and drives like a dream. It\u2019s got plenty of life left in it and is perfect for anyone who wants a dependable ride that still looks sharp on the road. Come by and take it for a spin, you're going to love how it handles!",
