    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously cared for and remains in impressive form, offering a perfect blend of performance and everyday utility. The exterior finish retains a deep, healthy gloss, complemented by clean lines, though you may find the occasional minor stone chip consistent with careful road use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the seating surfaces show only light natural creasing, and all electronic features\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system\u2014operate flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is robust. It has followed a strict preventative maintenance schedule, resulting in a quiet idle, smooth gear transitions, and responsive braking. Recent service includes a fresh oil change and a multi-point inspection, ensuring it is turn-key ready for its next owner. This is a reliable, high-quality choice for someone who values a well-documented service history and a car that drives as good as it looks.",
